.container.lead
  .row
    .col-md-10.col-md-push-1
      p We pride ourselves on providing the most reliable residential snow removal service in GTA's West End. Clearmysnow has been operating since 2006, but the management behind it has been providing property maintenance services for over 25 years.
      p Aside from our experience, we are also well equipped to handle nature’s elements and to weather any storm - with an ever-growing fleet of trucks, tractors, plows, blowers, shovels, salt-supplies and more than a dozen staff on-call, we can tackle every snowstorm that Canada has to offer.

